[{"conversations": [{"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110038_story/VO_CHR_110038_STORY_0023.wav"], "content": "唉～累死了，真是……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0043.wav"], "content": "嗯……？你在這裡做什麼啊？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0030.wav"], "content": "這附近的森林，到了晚上就會有魔獸出沒，趁現在趕快回去比較好喔。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110038_story/VO_CHR_110038_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "啊～是這樣嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110038_story/VO_CHR_110038_STORY_0024.wav"], "content": "可是就算叫我回去……我現在正在旅行耶。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "那麼，你還沒決定今晚住哪裡嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110038_story/VO_CHR_110038_STORY_0033.wav"], "content": "不是的，我要走到村落，然後預定借宿在那邊的教會。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110038_story/VO_CHR_110038_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "因為我姑且是個祭司實習生。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110038_story/VO_CHR_110038_STORY_0023.wav"], "content": "可是，要去村落感覺好累……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110038_story/VO_CHR_110038_STORY_0025.wav"], "content": "借住教會的話，又要講道跟聽人懺悔，好麻煩……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110038_story/VO_CHR_110038_STORY_0031.wav"], "content": "對了，小哥。這附近有可以住宿的地方嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "除了教會以外。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0012.wav"], "content": "我住的城就在這附近，你可以借住，可是……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0039.wav"], "content": "……你不去教會行嗎？不是還有祭司的工作……？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "沒關係啦，那只不過是一堆麻煩事而已。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110038_story/VO_CHR_110038_STORY_0028.wav"], "content": "而且……我也不是自願想當祭司實習生的。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110038_story/VO_CHR_110038_STORY_0012.wav"], "content": "比起這個，我們趕快去城堡吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110038_story/VO_CHR_110038_STORY_0016.wav"], "content": "好厲害～好氣派的城堡……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "小哥，你真的住在這座城裡嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "是啊。我姑且算是這座城的主人呢。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110038_story/VO_CHR_110038_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "主人？你是說這座氣派的城堡是你的嗎！？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "咦，小哥，你到底是何方神聖？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "這麼說來，我還沒自我介紹啊。我叫尤蒂爾。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110038_story/VO_CHR_110038_STORY_0022.wav"], "content": "尤蒂爾，是那個王族的！？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "那麼這座城裡，也住著侍奉王族的騎士囉！？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "嗯，是啊，也有其他人就是了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110038_story/VO_CHR_110038_STORY_0017.wav"], "content": "好厲害……！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "那個……我叫霍普！竟然能遇到真正的王族，深感光榮！！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0073.wav"], "content": "啊……啊啊。請多關照囉，霍普。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "不過，你怎麼了？為什麼突然那麼激動。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110038_story/VO_CHR_110038_STORY_0073.wav"], "content": "因為我很興奮啊！我的夢想，就是成為守護王族的真正的騎士！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "咦……？可是，你不是說你是祭司實習生嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110038_story/VO_CHR_110038_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "祭司實習生是……因為我爸媽是祭司，他們叫我要「繼承衣缽」，所以才強迫我去當的。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110038_story/VO_CHR_110038_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "可是比起當祭司，我其實更想成為為了守護他人而賭上性命的騎士！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "那個，拜託你！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "別只讓我住一晚，可以讓我暫時留在這座城裡嗎！？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "我想要親眼見識真正的騎士作戰的樣子！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110038_story/VO_CHR_110038_STORY_0010.wav"], "content": "要是你肯留下我，我願意做任何事！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "啊，好啊……我是沒關係啦。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110038_story/VO_CHR_110038_STORY_0001.wav"], "content": "太好了！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110038_story/VO_CHR_110038_STORY_0012.wav"], "content": "那我馬上去練習空揮！我會以騎士身份，助你一臂之力！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0033.wav"], "content": "不，先麻煩你去做打掃祭壇的工作吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "以祭司實習生的身分。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110038_story/VO_CHR_110038_STORY_0074.wav"], "content": "咦咦！？還以為終於可以進行騎士修行了……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}], "id": 110038011, "title": "想成為騎士的祭司實習生"}, {"conversations": [{"audioPaths": [], "content": "──敵人像這樣砍過來時，我就要這樣避開，然後在回頭的瞬間再這樣……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100002_story/VO_CHR_100002_STORY_0025.wav"], "content": "霍普，別拿著杖在祭壇揮來揮去，你到底在做什麼啊。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "啊……耶魯菲莉絲前輩！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100002_story/VO_CHR_100002_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "前、前輩……！？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110038_story/VO_CHR_110038_STORY_0031.wav"], "content": "是的！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "我總有一天會放棄當什麼祭司，然後成為騎士！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110038_story/VO_CHR_110038_STORY_0004.wav"], "content": "或許有點心急了，但因為妳是位出色的騎士，是我的目標，所以才稱呼妳為前輩！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110038_story/VO_CHR_110038_STORY_0012.wav"], "content": "對了。我剛才是在模擬實戰情況並試著應對！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "如何？還像樣嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100002_story/VO_CHR_100002_STORY_0023.wav"], "content": "……比起那個，你應該有其他事要做吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "打掃祭壇的工作，不是交給你負責了嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110038_story/VO_CHR_110038_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "啊～……那件事晚點再做啦。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110038_story/VO_CHR_110038_STORY_0030.wav"], "content": "為了成為騎士的訓練可重要多了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "對了！耶魯菲莉絲前輩，身為騎士，妳做了哪些訓練啊？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "我想要當作參考，請讓我見識見識吧！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100002_story/VO_CHR_100002_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "你呀，是想以這個為藉口，逃避打掃工作吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110038_story/VO_CHR_110038_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "嗚……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100002_story/VO_CHR_100002_STORY_0025.wav"], "content": "真是的……你並不是騎士，而是祭司。要完成自己的工作。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110038_story/VO_CHR_110038_STORY_0025.wav"], "content": "……可是，祭司的工作，就算做了也沒什麼意義不是嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100002_story/VO_CHR_100002_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "沒意義……？那是什麼意思。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110038_story/VO_CHR_110038_STORY_0062.wav"], "content": "祭司什麼的，不是在講道時間講些好聽話，就是聽人懺悔後，說著無聊的道理……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110038_story/VO_CHR_110038_STORY_0023.wav"], "content": "基本上都是在做這些事不是嗎？實際上根本沒有任何幫助。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……我並不這麼認為。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110038_story/VO_CHR_110038_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "我不想成為祭司。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "我更想成為……能夠守護別人的男人。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "對於持劍戰鬥、以身為盾，我都已經有所覺悟了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110038_story/VO_CHR_110038_STORY_0010.wav"], "content": "我想將我的生命，用在守護別人上！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "………………原來如此，你有那樣的心態，實在很了不起。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100002_story/VO_CHR_100002_STORY_0023.wav"], "content": "但是霍普，我不認為連自己的工作都無法好好完成的人，能成為一個出色的騎士。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110038_story/VO_CHR_110038_STORY_0038.wav"], "content": "唔……說得、也是……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110038_story/VO_CHR_110038_STORY_0023.wav"], "content": "既然耶魯菲莉絲前輩那麼說……雖然很麻煩，但我還是會打掃的。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……不過，好吧，等你打掃結束後，我可以陪你進行騎士訓練喔。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "咦……那、那是、真的嗎！？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100002_story/VO_CHR_100002_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "是啊，因為你想守護別人的心意，似乎是貨真價實的。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "但是……你可別誤會了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100002_story/VO_CHR_100002_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "我無法贊成，你想放棄祭司工作，成為騎士的目標──", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110038_story/VO_CHR_110038_STORY_0045.wav"], "content": "謝謝妳！我會馬上把祭壇掃得乾乾淨淨的！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110038_story/VO_CHR_110038_STORY_0012.wav"], "content": "訓練的事，就麻煩妳了！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100002_story/VO_CHR_100002_STORY_0025.wav"], "content": "……唉。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "看來光用口說，並無法阻止你對騎士的嚮往呢。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}], "id": 110038012, "title": "想要守護他人的心意"}, {"conversations": [{"audioPaths": [], "content": "嘎啊啊啊啊啊！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120007_01.png", "speakerName": "魔獸", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0055.wav"], "content": "哈啊！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0050.wav"], "content": "耶魯菲莉絲！就是現在！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100002_story/VO_CHR_100002_STORY_1012.wav"], "content": "交給我！哈啊啊啊啊啊！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120007_01.png", "speakerName": "魔獸", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100002_story/VO_CHR_100002_STORY_0024.wav"], "content": "呼……總算收拾掉了。你沒受傷吧，尤蒂爾？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0012.wav"], "content": "嗯。多虧了耶魯菲莉絲在我身後守護我，謝謝妳。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100002_story/VO_CHR_100002_STORY_1033.wav"], "content": "別在意，這是身為騎士該做的事。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110038_story/VO_CHR_110038_STORY_0017.wav"], "content": "為守護主君而戰的騎士……果然很帥氣……！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "啊，那個！　尤蒂爾王子！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "下次，請讓我也一起參與戰鬥！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110038_story/VO_CHR_110038_STORY_0012.wav"], "content": "不管是劍還是槍，我一定能駕輕就熟的！　", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110038_story/VO_CHR_110038_STORY_0010.wav"], "content": "拜託了！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "咦……可是，你是祭司吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "在前線跟魔獸戰鬥，實在太危險了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110038_story/VO_CHR_110038_STORY_0033.wav"], "content": "沒那回事！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110038_story/VO_CHR_110038_STORY_0073.wav"], "content": "我已經受過耶魯菲莉絲前輩的基礎指導了！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100002_story/VO_CHR_100002_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "基礎指導？你只是被我痛打了一頓吧？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110038_story/VO_CHR_110038_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "嗚嗚……請別讓我想起那件事……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "而、而且耶魯菲莉絲前輩妳不是對我說了嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110038_story/VO_CHR_110038_STORY_0031.wav"], "content": "我想守護別人的心意，是貨真價實的！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "既然如此，也讓我參加戰鬥……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100002_story/VO_CHR_100002_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "我確實這樣說過。但守護他人的手段，並不是只有戰鬥而已。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……那是什麼意思？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100002_story/VO_CHR_100002_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "霍普，你覺得我之前為什麼要讓你握劍呢？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110038_story/VO_CHR_110038_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "咦……是為了指導我作為騎士的基礎吧？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110038_story/VO_CHR_110038_STORY_0031.wav"], "content": "那不是在教我以劍守護別人的方法嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100002_story/VO_CHR_100002_STORY_0035.wav"], "content": "不，不是的。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "我之前之所以讓你握劍……是為了讓你注意到無法用劍守護的事物。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110038_story/VO_CHR_110038_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "無法用劍守護的事物……？那是什麼？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "連這都不懂的話還說什麼要守護別人……你還早得很呢。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110038_story/VO_CHR_110038_STORY_0038.wav"], "content": "等、等一下。我完全不懂妳的意思。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100002_story/VO_CHR_100002_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "你再好好想一想吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "為什麼你不是拿劍或拿槍，而是拿著杖呢？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100002_story/VO_CHR_100002_STORY_0032.wav"], "content": "這是因為有劍與槍做不到，只有杖才能守護的事物。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "只有杖才能守護的事物……？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110038_story/VO_CHR_110038_STORY_0023.wav"], "content": "妳到底在說什麼？那種事……我完全不懂啊……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}], "id": 110038013, "title": "守護的手段"}, {"conversations": [{"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100002_story/VO_CHR_100002_STORY_0026.wav"], "content": "呼……呼……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100002_story/VO_CHR_100002_STORY_0038.wav"], "content": "那些可惡的魔獸……到底要追我們到什麼時候……！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0026.wav"], "content": "抱歉……耶魯菲莉絲、霍普。若只有你們的話，早就能逃脫了。", "isSys