alse, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110038_story/VO_CHR_110038_STORY_0031.wav"], "content": "只有拿著杖的祭司才做得到的事……！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……對了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110038_story/VO_CHR_110038_STORY_0071.wav"], "content": "我可以替尤蒂爾王子和耶魯菲莉絲前輩治療！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110038_story/VO_CHR_110038_STORY_0010.wav"], "content": "雖然在這裡只能做緊急處理，不過我會讓你們回復到能度過這個難關的。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110038_story/VO_CHR_110038_STORY_0026.wav"], "content": "呼……呼……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110038_story/VO_CHR_110038_STORY_0021.wav"], "content": "總算甩開魔獸了呢。累、累死了……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "是啊……霍普，你真的是幫了大忙。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "不過，要是不找個地方休息，大家的體力就要撐不住了……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100002_story/VO_CHR_100002_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "是的……在回城的路上，可能又會遇到魔獸。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100002_story/VO_CHR_100002_STORY_1027.wav"], "content": "去那座村子休息吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "喂，你們這些拿著武器的傢伙。不准再靠近村子了！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120014_01.png", "speakerName": "村民", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0037.wav"], "content": "請等一下。我們只是想在這裡休息一下。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "並沒有想要危害村民……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120014_story/VO_CHR_120014_STORY_0030.wav"], "content": "只是嘴上說說，想怎麼講都可以吧。你們要怎麼保證不會掠奪村子！？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120014_01.png", "speakerName": "村民", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "竟然如此警戒……啊！？這麼說來，最近好像多了不少假扮成旅人的盜賊，所以他們才會……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……吶，村民們，聽我說！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "我不是騎士也不是劍士，是祭司！就像你們所見，我沒有武器！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110038_story/VO_CHR_110038_STORY_0031.wav"], "content": "如果這些人開始掠奪的話……到時我就隨你們處置！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "所以拜託了！讓我們在村裡休息吧！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "霍普……！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120014_story/VO_CHR_120014_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "……祭司嗎。我知道了，就相信你們吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120014_01.png", "speakerName": "村民", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120014_story/VO_CHR_120014_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "但如果你的同伴開始胡來，我們會拿你當人質的。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120014_01.png", "speakerName": "村民", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0045.wav"], "content": "謝謝你，霍普。因為你的幫助，終於能稍微歇息了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0030.wav"], "content": "今天一直受到你的協助呢。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110038_story/VO_CHR_110038_STORY_0033.wav"], "content": "不，沒這種事……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110038_story/VO_CHR_110038_STORY_0035.wav"], "content": "無法與魔獸戰鬥的我，也只能做到這種事。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100002_story/VO_CHR_100002_STORY_0033.wav"], "content": "不，霍普。尤蒂爾說得沒錯。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100002_story/VO_CHR_100002_STORY_0045.wav"], "content": "有你這位祭司在，真是幫了我們很大的忙，謝謝你。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110038_story/VO_CHR_110038_STORY_0016.wav"], "content": "耶魯菲莉絲前輩……！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110038_story/VO_CHR_110038_STORY_0073.wav"], "content": "我……很高興能以祭司的身分協助你們！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}], "id": 110038014, "title": "祭司能做到的事"}, {"conversations": [{"audioPaths": [], "content": "──要是對方這樣砍過來，就這樣把劍彈開……在這瞬間刺過去！好，就是這樣。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100002_story/VO_CHR_100002_STORY_0023.wav"], "content": "霍普……又在祭壇模仿騎士了嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100002_story/VO_CHR_100002_STORY_0025.wav"], "content": "打掃工作呢？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110038_story/VO_CHR_110038_STORY_0073.wav"], "content": "打掃工作我已經完成囉。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "騎士訓練的話，這個嘛，已經算是我的習慣了吧……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0032.wav"], "content": "的確，連一點灰塵都沒有呢。挺厲害的嘛。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "不過你怎麼會突然這麼認真的打掃呢？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110038_story/VO_CHR_110038_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "啊～該怎麼說～我……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110038_story/VO_CHR_110038_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "有點那個，想要認真地以成為祭司為目標了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0012.wav"], "content": "這樣啊！雖然這樣很棒沒錯……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "不過之前比起祭司，你更想當騎士的不是嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "怎麼會突然有這種想法？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110038_story/VO_CHR_110038_STORY_0062.wav"], "content": "就是啊……之前……在跟魔獸對戰時，我發現了一件事。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "治療受傷的夥伴，以及從害怕爭鬥的人們那裡獲得信任，這些事……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110038_story/VO_CHR_110038_STORY_0030.wav"], "content": "都是騎士辦不到，只有祭司才能做到的。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110038_story/VO_CHR_110038_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "我現在仍對騎士有所嚮往，但是……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "正因為如此，比起騎士，我現在更想要成為一名祭司。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110038_story/VO_CHR_110038_STORY_0073.wav"], "content": "總有一天，我要成為出色的祭司……成為能夠守護我所嚮往的騎士的存在。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "霍普……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100002_story/VO_CHR_100002_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "原來如此……我會全力支持你追求目標的！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100002_story/VO_CHR_100002_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "……雖說如此，既然你真心想成為祭司，那你就得離開這座城了對吧……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "啊～關於那件事……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110038_story/VO_CHR_110038_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "如果可以的話，我想要繼續留在這裡。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "可是……留在這座城，可以累積擔任祭司的經驗嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "我來到這座城後……感覺到自己以祭司的身分，獲得了很大的成長。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110038_story/VO_CHR_110038_STORY_0023.wav"], "content": "畢竟在我以祭司實習生身份旅行時，可是絕對不會想成為祭司的……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "但在這座城待了一段時間後，卻開始認真地想要成為祭司了耶？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110038_story/VO_CHR_110038_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "所以，我覺得……若想累積當祭司的經驗，繼續待在這座城是最好的選擇。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "而且啊，大家不是常常會在戰場上受傷嗎。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110038_story/VO_CHR_110038_STORY_0024.wav"], "content": "若要累積治癒魔法的經驗，也沒有比這裡更適合的地方了吧……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110038_story/VO_CHR_110038_STORY_0031.wav"], "content": "所以說……王子，拜託你！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110038_story/VO_CHR_110038_STORY_0012.wav"], "content": "請讓我繼續在這裡修行吧！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0012.wav"], "content": "當然沒有問題。往後也請多多指教了，霍普。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100002_story/VO_CHR_100002_STORY_0012.wav"], "content": "有你在，我也能安心作戰了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "拜託你囉，霍普。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110038_story/VO_CHR_110038_STORY_0073.wav"], "content": "嘿嘿……耶魯菲莉絲前輩。尤蒂爾王子，我會繼續努力的！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "我一定會以這把杖，守護兩位……不，守護這座城的所有人！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110038_01.png", "speakerName": "霍普", "type": "conversation"}], "id": 110038015, "title": "為了保護憧憬的騎士"}]